import React from 'react'
import HeroMain from './HeroMain'
import LoginForm from './HerosLogin'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

const App = () => {

  const [token,setToken] = useStat()

  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Switch>
        <Route path="/login">
          <LoginForm />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/heros"> 
          <HeroMain title= {"Bienvenido a tu pagina de héroes!"}/>
        </Route>
      </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
